                <h1>Understanding Islam: Faith, Culture, and Community</h1>
                <p>Islam, one of the world's major religions, emphasizes the belief in one God (Allah) and the teachings of the Prophet Muhammad. Followers, known as Muslims, practice the Five Pillars: faith, prayer, charity, fasting, and pilgrimage. Its diverse cultures and interpretations showcase a rich history, promoting peace and community worldwide.</p>
